  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c8e61516-855a-4a6b-bc3c-b7c27fd37cf5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4d327060-dfa7-4c90-b738-59008d15c54c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-db5831f9-0966-41a2-b5a6-8ee2561f29f1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ce3e65df-149c-4bdd-b2ab-343082940227\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b6ee2c70-a846-43c9-8108-56b9d055409f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0d6a4b0e-7bd8-41cb-9253-e4c3b3d988be\" style=\"color:#000000;\">여행은 누구와 함께 떠나는가에 따라 그 의미가 달라지죠. 많은 분들이 효도 여행을 고민할 때 제주도 여행을 떠올리는데요. 자연 속에서 여유롭게 시간을 보내며 함께 추억을 쌓기에는 제주만 한 곳이 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4657e687-75e2-423c-b650-de9df21ea2b5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8b00d707-eafa-4d8b-904c-2bdeb699e6a6\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e0eba189-949b-48bc-9d96-4ee6c677e112\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-283cc873-45f0-4b32-a0f0-3191dbe60202\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-39ec6272-92f4-4ac5-a75e-3b581df8348f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d062ce4b-1e91-456a-ba77-99665fb2a7e5\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d0ed8868-5044-4a83-93ab-e0f4d6d8095f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-da8a4957-f093-4a8c-afa4-42c8b93d6cbe\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><i>그렇지만 엄마와 단둘이 여행을 계획할 때는 고민할 것들이 많습니다. </i></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6e77bed0-404e-4601-a17d-3a2117baf71d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>이번 글에서는 엄마와 꼭 함께 가봐야 할 제주도 명소와 그곳에서 남긴 추억을 어떻게 특별하게 간직할 수 있는지 소개해 드리겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-81108174-de96-4b51-b22c-b46258cddcf6\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c3227257-cb8d-4170-bdb6-bf52297017bc\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-94bba631-4d15-465e-bfca-0df27062d5b3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb12c14f-8437-46b0-8852-b17b9d1f7cdc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3c015760-eedf-4087-a02f-0ee44a7d3cfe\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>엄마와 제주도 여행지 어떻게 선택해야 할까?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ff287c49-7cb5-479e-a915-2b427047992b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4b1b99e3-a22e-4101-92ad-5b346c039d8d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-47ea4d22-84d7-4b1d-9b12-0a677b5915fa\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a8a3653d-951c-4cac-aba7-42dd3b130bc8\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-64faa5ed-1e1b-4a51-98ec-33965979adca\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-86b715fc-e953-48b7-b9e4-ce9563c26733\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">제</span>주도는 걸음이 편안하고, 중간에 쉬어갈 수 있는 장소가 많아 부모님과 함께 여행하기 좋은 곳입니다. 하지만 부모님과의 여행에서는 몇 가지 고려할 사항이 있는데요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6d8fadc0-f4f5-4961-8111-8e4924b9863f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-869fc741-87a6-4a0a-ba52-5ae4ab179e6e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1be0575b-aca9-44c3-a215-91340da8f01a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3884a82b-7018-409b-b3a5-4c1b6a1a6d98\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>우선, 걷는 거리가 너무 길지 않아야 부모님께서 무리 없이 걸으실 수 있고, 휴식할 수 있는 벤치나 카페 같은 공간이 잘 마련되어 있어야 합니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-259dc2df-7c3a-47b3-bccf-13ac17d3ef20\" style=\"color:#000000;\">또한</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2df37a06-9b89-4070-99cc-375af01f3667\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b> 사람이 많이 붐비지 않는 한적한 장소</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e664e1e8-0abf-4325-b8ba-37a995e96a37\" style=\"color:#000000;\">를 선택하면 엄마와 오붓하게 이야기를 나누기에도 좋습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-95558e03-c3b5-4176-8617-4d68f7971808\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e2a72332-7f4b-47ba-891a-a3ecbe7e1881\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-abd934fc-0da8-44ce-95b5-b92e49a1d433\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ea0eeec5-e2da-4841-b4f2-2d83f56953c9\" style=\"color:#000000;\">이러한 장소를 중심으로 코스를 짠다면, 여행의 피로를 줄이면서도 소중한 추억을 남길 수 있답니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-252f57a6-fc38-49cf-a504-839d4e602110\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3bb49678-227b-42ec-86ce-b18cfefbb798\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7b684232-5ef9-4104-a5b9-168a9d100ed7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c58614e4-07e0-4272-9b23-b50d1e79ebaf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-daac2aee-076e-4e94-9730-448aa30a63e7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>제주도 추천 여행지: 사진 찍기 좋은 곳</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-47aefd7d-09f1-4417-bfde-d935969e3262\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4be882ff-7d5f-4c1f-8bb3-5e187f28916d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5c1a52c9-96e0-4b17-ae63-765e78932d5e\" style=\"\">1. 비밀의 숲 - 동화 속에 들어온 듯한 신비로운 숲길</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-211c7628-7729-407e-a19b-8c09ff18ba4a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-351cf514-8ca7-4fc3-adbc-49a221e600b5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2d3b979a-c2c2-4b7a-ab71-25588d005c6c\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c8732e72-f478-4c59-92b8-c21402a99809\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-6b9bdaf3-de25-4448-abc7-648e9b204061\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4e28fb68-47f0-415f-a5ff-19961c5870e0\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">제</span>주시 구좌읍 송당리에 위치한 '비밀의 숲'은 이름만큼이나 신비로운 분위기를 자아낸답니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-14a4e87b-bda7-477e-a756-3c11b00c98fb\" style=\"color:#000000;\">울창한 편백나무와 삼나무 숲이 이어진 산책로는 걸을 때마다 상쾌한 나무 향이 가득합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-db6800e5-cd6a-462b-9d34-6fd67b30e26e\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-948d992b-b813-4e57-b069-95fb3ab8c1ab\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f28cdf23-d344-404e-a7d5-b4957c814016\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-878398f7-8ae5-43db-806a-1f795a61ab01\" style=\"color:#000000;\">평탄한 길로 이루어져 있어 부모님과 함께 천천히 걸으며 이야기를 나누기에 참 좋답니다. 엄마와 손을 맞잡고 걷다 보면 자연스레 추억이 쌓이고, 서로의 이야기를 들으며 가까워지는 시간을 가질 수 있을 텐데요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7fc15f14-fd00-4f7b-83bd-9a58eb1b8978\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-11f44cc1-6867-4e76-8881-f89d849306bb\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2879b68c-a64b-40bc-8569-9b9de0a9c0bd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9a84c144-94bf-41e8-b57a-c335a114787b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-784a6e44-77ab-4c65-9a34-f6bee2dc8e8a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-591c869e-745b-4311-af1b-6560830cfb4e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-88e6f74d-fe7a-4182-bc22-689342a45b7d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1c061b1c-a315-495e-85a4-abfb8dc6dcdd\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>곳곳에 포토존이 마련되어 있어 엄마와 함께 자연 속에서 추억을 남기기에 제격이에요. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-de4288e5-6667-44ac-8a7a-7d6abec8d784\" style=\"color:#000000;\">이곳에서 찍은 사진들은 마치 동화 속에 들어온 듯한 느낌을 남기다 보니, 시간이 흘러도 그날의 따뜻한 기억이 떠오를 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-46b08b3c-5a50-4e23-b954-a5a7498667ea\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-76f08547-918d-48b6-98f7-0b19643eef3a\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-355dcfb8-2e0e-484c-abe8-0804c3e012b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b2105f27-b1c0-4a92-ae36-fbc8092f25a2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-02bf7e38-a5bd-4bb0-9ce9-a1da94e53774\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>2. 성산일출봉 - 제주 바다를 한눈에 담다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6fea05bf-e74e-479f-862c-d62cc8da605e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6c82b837-8e44-49b0-916b-3a4e8a7ce4c9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-760a3633-6eda-401b-9848-f3788393fbf4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a41a4b00-5e09-415b-a54d-25632be9592b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-ee3a7135-b6c6-46b1-8311-d0810da33490\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a61d0168-efc9-4bb7-ad7b-11f9848c6c13\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">제</span>주도의 대표적인 명소 중 하나인 성산 일출봉은 부모님과 함께하기에 안성맞춤인 곳입니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7c9fb6a4-e0b5-48d8-b33c-76e714ee2653\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 해발 180m에 위치한 성산일출봉 정상에 오르면 넓은 분화구와 함께 제주 바다의 광활한 풍경이 펼쳐지는데요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3fd163e6-9d5c-47eb-b70d-f754e3d0323f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b22e8c2f-727e-474f-8fe2-5e9023b4528c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2052ee33-4450-472e-9afa-8b5cbafef20c\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4eee5fda-d7b8-4c9b-b849-fe184f3fd456\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><i>그러나 부모님과 함께라면 굳이 정상까지 오르지 않아도 충분히 멋진 경관을 만끽할 수 있습니다.</i></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-07fccb00-62df-4cc4-b334-7d5a96e34616\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 중턱에 마련된 전망대만으로도 바다와 분화구가 어우러진 절경을 볼 수 있는데요. 약 20분 정도의 가벼운 산책으로도 이 멋진 풍경을 감상할 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a85c1e53-d6d0-4711-815f-8f990615d2e4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-972007ad-700d-47ad-82e0-6158b2bf8383\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-40bf8a9e-6bba-4c8c-89ae-15864be96fb0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c7abbc08-2dca-4fac-b09f-f77d7dbfd585\" style=\"color:#000000;\">부모님의 체력에 부담이 가지 않으면서도 넉넉한 시간을 보낼 수 있답니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0d72d33b-a529-4646-906b-0bbd760214a5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-bb8196d0-9d30-42d3-b925-5faa0d7138ac\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9d99366d-b3e0-4288-81aa-245e95d8f392\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8719dd74-b6bb-452e-847e-596b7ee9a47e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6aec1d54-0223-4e84-84ce-d5e593906433\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cdfe2bb8-291f-4ee6-a292-426f457aeac4\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8beaa376-ace9-4aa9-810f-030eeced733c\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5be5ba71-2105-4519-a780-fe3d03f34f75\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><i>그리고 굳이 산을 오르지 않아도 되는데요. 바닷가 쪽에서 바라보는 성산 일출봉의 모습 역시 사진으로 남기기에 충분히 아름답기 때문이죠.</i></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4c5c334f-824e-422b-9439-b06637a31766\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 성산일출봉 주변에서 엄마와 함께 걸으며 나눈 이야기와 그 순간의 미소는 시간이 지나도 오래도록 기억에 남을 소중한 추억이 될 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-66838669-a7dd-4d1d-a7ed-2e03f3e2ef26\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7c68890f-1e99-42aa-9d26-75db4ce56603\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-62c373cd-a24c-4882-8d64-dfb33b08c6c6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dcf0445a-cb91-4370-981a-842e41f74f40\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-090c952d-83c9-45d6-a5e2-a42ebe8b0212\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>3. 제주 돌 문화공원 - 제주의 역사와 문화를 한눈에</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ce9615c3-73e3-4f31-ab8c-34e6783aace9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f7a5458f-157d-48e2-8b4a-7163d82396e7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-10b81859-fdde-476b-96e8-0a34e07fccf9\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-85b29803-1f93-4926-b536-49d427c24d9e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-2a589965-4038-466c-8bac-a00b26f14510\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-609bf299-ad3f-41a0-b935-f0ce35e6ef4f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">제</span>주의 전통 돌문화를 집대성한 제주 돌 문화공원도 부모님과의 여행에 좋은 장소인데요. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d2fde546-883a-41e4-8ba2-ba5686156e2a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">오백장군의 전설을 비롯해 제주의 역사와 문화를 한눈에 볼 수 있는 곳으로, 평탄한 산책로가 잘 정비되어 있어 편안하게 걸으며 이야기를 나눌 수 있답니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92836c81-b826-42ba-b2c8-0a071ecfdbe8\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c8bd3c51-290c-420b-9b99-517e09be8b58\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fbb586a2-606e-44cd-8e2c-3d01e1805515\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9054d1e5-228b-4a57-9c4e-de4cace257f6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-61aa9ed2-b024-4ecb-a5e3-e1475199156e\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-aef7a4aa-31dc-4d9f-aa58-6cad098ab13b\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-61975a0b-d4a7-475f-b632-ba5a0f461686\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-69abf872-227d-4298-9198-dab4274432b0\" style=\"color:#000000;\">특히 제주의 독특한 돌 문화를 가까이에서 느낄 수 있어 색다른 경험이 될 텐데요. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fe62b1a8-5c07-43ea-a14a-66653f896aa6\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><i>제주의 전통 가옥과 돌조각들을 둘러보며 엄마와 함께 소소한 이야기를 나누다 보면, 마치 시간 여행을 떠난 듯한 기분이 들기도 한답니다. </i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8eed4708-fac1-4f76-b7ec-f4855ef730b0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9b93888f-6d7f-4508-a872-9d8e9581675d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e192b8d7-f7e8-4b54-b1bf-dda724cb8f22\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ec2f0f5d-9e55-40ae-ba37-582dd002d725\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>산책로가 평탄하게 정비되어 있어 천천히 걸으며 둘러보기 좋고, 곳곳에 마련된 포토존에서 사진을 찍으면 마치 그날의 이야기가 사진 속에 담기는 듯한 느낌을 받습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c7fa6b5d-40f6-4655-a1a1-4a3f56eb73ed\" style=\"color:#000000;\">전시된 돌조각들과 전통적인 건축물들을 배경으로 사진을 남기면, 그 순간이 고스란히 추억으로 남게 되겠지요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-46758792-8fd6-43c5-b90a-35eea6ed8ef0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fd94658c-d428-441b-b247-1dbd466e358f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-ab22bb03-09fc-4474-affd-16f955102d58\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10223292-abaf-4f22-9144-e4a03d6731ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-df3a69ed-2f1e-43ff-b3ef-9d9027b72eec\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>여행에서 중요한 것 (엄마와의 대화법, 사진 잘 찍어 주는 법)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53ab1a63-c4e8-4b52-88c3-99ddfe3f8507\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dbd68a19-a6be-4955-a5b0-f9c78a210435\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2fc38bea-6c60-4510-a3b1-3258dd624c2a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-85f262df-b98f-46d7-97de-ec5145870906\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-a03adce6-4073-4811-80ec-c77a7091b1f3\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c2aaf859-099b-4b89-9f30-a699d5582fb7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">그</span>런데 여행 중에 무엇보다 중요한 건 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4bfce727-871b-4ae7-88be-7462746506a0\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>엄마와의 대화</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5cf13c97-31e8-404a-82a0-bc156f548705\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>입니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a98ec886-6865-4577-9910-a4fe6d6ad832\" style=\"color:#000000;\">여행지의 아름다움을 함께 느끼는 것도 좋지만, 그 속에서 오롯이 서로의 이야기를 나누는 시간은 무엇과도 바꿀 수 없는 소중한 추억이 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ba975f12-4e0d-4e93-a138-77f9fb2ecd6b\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-dc51f2e8-d882-4118-a625-62454dfbb012\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a987de32-6fd0-48f6-bf78-ac7eeaeded04\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-56881c8e-d958-4764-8fdc-b3494f440864\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><i><b>평소에는 바쁘다는 이유로 묻지 못했던 이야기들, 엄마가 좋아했던 어린 시절 추억이나 요즘 관심 있는 것들에 대해 차분히 들어보세요. 그런 대화를 통해 서로의 마음을 더 깊이 이해할 수 있고, 여행의 의미도 더욱 커지게 될 겁니다.</b></i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8452e491-7eee-4282-bdb9-7e8ac7c933db\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3c9123a2-2fbd-4ac8-9ee3-853c1344dfd4\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-49277b26-e705-4040-a5d1-5f6caf4b7d6a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e5bbe424-a539-475d-868f-6545faa25df1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4ce735a4-ea79-4c6f-9466-18dbaea1ac2f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fd82b30a-dd29-4ccf-ae5f-ef89b176dd3c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-425cd75a-d5d9-4ff8-a15d-fb42e6d8b606\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c9ad926e-762a-449b-ac97-a9c35b219a1b\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">그</span>리고 엄마와의 추억을 잘 남기기 위해 사진도 잘 찍어드리면 좋겠죠.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-007a6986-997f-480c-a0f3-37695b84c919\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9476fbbf-8f6a-42cf-963c-871f9f21cf29\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>사진을 찍을 때는 자연광을 잘 활용하고, 다양한 각도에서 촬영해 보세요.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-61df9de9-cb33-4329-b26c-902e56b34b13\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b3658e17-641b-4230-9bf3-d76664e884b4\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><i>엄마가 웃는 순간, 무언가에 집중하는 순간들을 자연스럽게 담아낸다면 평생 간직하고 싶은 사진이 될 거예요. </i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-af1459e8-2688-4fa3-973b-feb8c92e59d0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5a78d1cf-f5a9-4c01-a712-0fbdc28b4be7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d74ea5c6-d6f1-4089-87da-884b14c5b898\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4c8ec6c4-3dd7-4a88-8122-daea8ab65d0d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">사진을 찍을 때는 한 번에 많은 컷을 찍어보는 것도 좋은 방법입니다. 자연스러운 모습 중에서도 예쁜 순간을 포착할 수 있고, 선택의 폭도 넓어지니까요. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-43f3c392-522f-4438-b6e2-152aa70846b7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><i>또한 배경을 신경 쓰면 사진의 분위기가 한층 더 살아나니, 그날의 추억을 더욱 아름답게 기록할 수 있을 거예요.</i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-90a8d687-d524-44dc-ad58-326c5c72b5d1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5d9d51e2-49e0-4650-8e26-73f4a2210d97\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-316b624c-d907-412e-983c-cc640232007d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-80fbbdae-4fa8-4af7-a6a3-17118181adc6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-48add326-2e1b-4f75-8395-f5a9e9f1c542\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>여행 후, 사진은 어떻게 보관할까? 포토북으로 간직하는 추억</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-076f431c-5abf-442e-ad54-008ab4070a1e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6835b99a-5e86-4213-9e55-2c5a7876ad7b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-94e709ac-45a2-422b-8d91-b8fc5bd708f3\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-07a98b40-6207-495e-8dc3-5d34d9a872b6\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-9d25a71b-96e6-4cdc-9c74-aa7105782135\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-aeb82174-53e4-40c0-8489-8542d1f1dad1\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">여</span>행 중 찍은 수많은 사진들, 혹시 아직도 핸드폰 앨범 속에만 남겨두고 계시나요? 시간이 지나면 소중했던 추억들이 잊히기 마련입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e373e5f2-f29a-4b83-b8d6-98467dfbf657\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8b6346cb-3740-40ee-b32e-e1e51c490037\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-481c3cdf-1054-4b0f-ac59-38c0ca73c884\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3a15118f-350f-4ed2-a0cc-3fecc2bc2736\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>그래서 추천드리는 것이 바로 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1c41dc1f-1e1d-439e-a378-d7b94f2e226f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>포토북</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0c5f7f3f-a138-4003-bc87-34484178b327\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>입니다. 특히 점보포토 포토북은 단순히 사진을 인쇄하는 것이 아니라, 여행의 흐름과 감정을 한 권의 책으로 엮어주기 때문에 넘길 때마다 그날의 대화, 웃음소리가 생생하게 떠오르죠.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e783036d-eecf-4ca9-8016-6f66baa3feb9\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a3f48a3e-fe76-401c-953c-b7d83462b391\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-877b4f84-d2b9-42a1-8234-0ab97a029cf9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0524d4a-4773-418f-a68f-0988c8ea7007\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ee7c184f-1c20-4348-9d38-b7123076709c\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-868d7c56-cbca-4f0e-81c9-7645d5642787\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-e12ae635-8251-4b36-b699-4817078ab775\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4b55e485-56ea-46c7-84b1-5a8062d4ac5e\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">점</span>보포토 포토북은 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-33be52af-f980-46b1-8279-bf77cc7b336c\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>후지필름 QPDP 정품 인화지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0bcd1ce4-99f9-439a-8c2c-0df22758b416\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>를 사용해 고화질로 인쇄되고, 유광 또는 무광 코팅 옵션을 제공해 오랫동안 빛바램 없이 보관할 수 있습니다. 특히 점보포토는 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-905e4795-1ba2-4aa9-afa4-c000f145a53c\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>업계 유일의 UV 유광 코팅을 무료</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0497a274-b512-4ac9-94df-b243777e61a6\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>로 제공하여 시간이 지나도 변색 없이 선명한 사진을 간직할 수 있답니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-64dd466e-13dd-475e-aa98-74afacfe24b9\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-189ebed9-e39a-4087-ad76-6d40d84f5e45\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bc0a284-ceec-4038-b8cc-6eff50486d7b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/013.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3e13bd9-bbf3-4bd2-9d39-86ef28250971\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8a105de2-aa30-42ae-831d-50615c117ef1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-76184e21-8d5e-4e4a-8ea2-d4068f211f95\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-bc8a25b7-09f6-4eac-95a7-4bd2a1349835\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-266ee5eb-71bf-4bcf-b6c0-0255b1989b67\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">편</span>집 툴도 사용하기 쉬워, 템플릿 선택 후 간단히 사진만 올리면 깔끔하고 예쁜 포토북이 완성됩니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f844bbdf-9b3f-48ba-9044-3f0fe662812c\" style=\"color:#000000;\">사진 레이아웃 변경, 스티커와 텍스트 추가 등 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9ba7894f-6a42-4be4-98b2-64f88f38f461\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>초보자도 손쉽게 다룰 수 있는 인터페이스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cb9b75ef-d845-4e32-8001-02dfa4d04581\" style=\"color:#000000;\">가 준비되어 있어, 부모님과의 추억을 한 권에 담기 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3da911ff-f0fd-4893-9648-33ff6a59f388\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3032bed0-8438-496f-95b6-d86e9af0b56f\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9ff33006-b2c8-4016-aa50-7fe2f0a3eecb\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-82104ea2-bfe3-4340-b950-a34b8ac2bbec\" style=\"color:#000000;\">간편하게 제작후 주문하면 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f9fc1960-5af9-4f70-a533-caaf97c7827e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>출력 &gt; 표지코팅 &gt; 표지코팅 후 표지만들기 &gt; 내지코팅 &gt; 성책 단계</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4004d113-f8f6-41e3-8644-ceb432e54f3d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">를 거쳐서 완성되고 신속하게 배달됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-291605c6-2b97-4ceb-bb03-e9d7abfe7c1d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fa723df9-96fe-4d21-a90c-5edd901e37aa\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-1822f617-dd1a-4d79-90a6-d60df2083622\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-58b89bab-58b4-4977-aefb-58989afcb528\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-06080eed-cfb4-438b-8745-94dfba146df4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-627d1908-2356-46a0-8a32-084fa93ca014\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ab4f86ab-a44f-483b-a98e-709a98e2fe65\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-91c621fe-8d1a-4f42-84ec-1e4fe37f18d3\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>무엇보다 점보포토는</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8a591f51-3311-4f46-b906-bb1a44dc1db8\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b> 100% 품질 보증 서비스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cd0907ac-9dd9-4c91-9e48-99bcedabeb8a\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>를 제공하기 때문에, 혹시 제작된 포토북에 문제가 생기더라도 새롭게 제작해 드리니 안심하고 추억을 간직할 수 있습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c73d1604-7b82-429b-b04c-918195a6e408\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 품질에 문제가 생길 경우 고객센터에 연락만 주시면 빠르게 처리되며, 처음부터 끝까지 고 퀄러티 상태로 제작된 포토북을 받아보실 수 있답니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7a550402-67b4-470a-b2d3-16a1a34923d6\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a5a2c8fc-b3b5-41d4-9e92-74bc1d4b36b5\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba533160-f9f3-4caf-a112-3f80550431c6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223859297195/014.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-95fbea08-e25f-4a0a-881a-11adffe3538e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4f5a525c-45dd-4543-a823-7a693de0c432\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-30b57bc9-33a4-4c67-97be-ed16e6fa8cbf\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-f1e8de9e-6482-4af4-97da-67495b6c3757\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fb5df9a7-32bb-4725-bf12-6e106a55b073\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">여</span>행에서 남긴 추억은 시간이 지나도 그날의 감동이 생생하게 되살아나야 의미가 있죠. 점보포토 포토북은 그날의 대화와 웃음을 그대로 담아, 책장을 넘길 때마다 따뜻한 기억이 피어오르게 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e94d65c9-bae6-4086-be85-47982efa70bc\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-13bbc3e3-a5b1-4a0b-a290-7879654416d6\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e99e0d48-bc44-4c35-9df0-2a4ef047fbd7\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2ec96c35-53e1-4255-a511-9dab6ede8962\" style=\"color:#000000;\">엄마와 함께한 제주 여행의 소중한 순간들을 한 권의 포토북으로 간직해 보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-942ae5ad-c54e-4c1e-96c6-90bf25df1055\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-da7d2267-24f9-485c-b48a-8706e19bd915\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-0c67203c-abf6-45f9-a053-751aabbb035b\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cfa9bd73-f425-40d6-9dc6-e05b966dc48f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5a41691-7787-47ed-a309-1bc447db1d93\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-435f0766-eef1-42df-bcd3-1adf19d021b6\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
